<title>NUMBERLESS AS THE STANDS OF THE SEA</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jordan luigala I kikhawp tieng leh,
 Hukdamte lopi takin mui tiu;
 Luipi panga pilnel simsen loh bang,
 Etnawp a um na lawmlawm ding e!

[V2]
 Luipi panga pilnel simsen loh bang!
 Luipanga pilnel simsen loh bang!
 Etnawpum tak hina, tatsate I muh tieng leh,
 Luipi panga pilnel simsen loh bangin.

[V3]
 2. Kumsawt a hukhinte cheng I muh tieng,
 Lungkhamna leh thepna cheng pelin;
 Lawp takin van a khun kituok hitiu,
 Etnawp a um na lawmlawm ding e!

[V4]
 3. Luipi hawih pang achun I din tieng leh,
 Hinna thingbak limah chawl hitiu;
 Gam tiem Kanaan gam nuom lam en hitiu,
 Etnawp a um na lawmlawm ding e!

[V5]
 4. I Tanpau deihtak chuh I muh tieng leh,
 Alopina nasat zie muitiu;
 Gam chengcheng Lal bang a vai A hawm tieng,
 Etnawp a um na lawmlawm ding e!</lyrics>
</song>